f whether they are receiving an acetylcholinesterase inhibitor.', 'Moderate', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/174375/', '', 'Ketotifen, Levocetirizine, Trimethobenzamide, Loratadine, Desloratadine, Azelastine', 'Ginkgo biloba, Aducanumab', 1767369485);
