mic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/174376/', '', 'Ketotifen, Levocetirizine, Cetirizine, Fexofenadine, Loratadine, Trimethobenzamide, Desloratadine, Azelastine, Terfenadine, Astemizole', '', 1767369485);
